## 1. Naming Conventions

### 1.1 File Naming

```yaml
Page YAML Config: {page_name}_page.yaml
  Examples: login_page.yaml, user_management_page.yaml

Page Object File: {page_name}_page.py
  Examples: login_page.py, user_management_page.py

Page Object Class: {PageName}Page (PascalCase)
  Examples: LoginPage, UserManagementPage

Handler File: {page_name}_handler.py
  Examples: login_handler.py, user_management_handler.py

Handler Class: {PageName}Handler (PascalCase)
  Examples: LoginHandler, UserManagementHandler

Test File: test_{page_name}_page.py
  Examples: test_login_page.py, test_user_management_page.py

Test Class: Test{PageName}Page
  Examples: TestLoginPage, TestUserManagementPage
```

### 1.2 Method Naming

```python
# PageObject class method naming
click_{element_name}_button()     # Click button
set_{element_name}_input(text)     # Input text
get_{element_name}_text()          # Get text
switch_to_{window_name}_window()   # Switch window
select_{element_name}_option()     # Select dropdown option
