## 5. BasePage Core Methods Reference

### 5.1 Element Locating (with Appium Caching)

```python
# Locate single element (with automatic caching)
element = self.locate_element(automation_id="btnLogin")
element = self.locate_element(automation_id="btnLogin", type="Button")
element = self.locate_element(name="确认", control_type="Button")

# Locate with cache control
element = self.locate_element(timeout=10, use_cache=True, automation_id="btnLogin")

# Disable cache for one-time locate
element = self.locate_element(use_cache=False, timeout=2, automation_id="btnLogin")

# Locate multiple elements
elements = self.locate_elements(xpath="//*[@Name='xxx']")
```

